{"tid":1106174,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 事前預約！高橋留美子正版授權《犬夜叉 奈落之戰》","createTime":"2019-04-14T11:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T09:45:58.000Z","uid":54085,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e813e0f22c04fb0b9cabcb16a383a4888d49254","tid":1106174,"uid":54085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"GameNuts 遊戲平台今日宣布，高橋留美子正版授權的 3D 動漫手機遊戲《犬夜叉 奈落之戰》開放 GooglePlay、AppStore 雙平台預約。此外，繼先前首次曝光角色技能玩法的影片後，今日也率先公開「許願樹系統」及一系列宣傳原畫。"},{"pid":"2828538283192f02ace3d11d4697df29ae5bb55a","tid":1106174,"uid":54085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=57nrMT351fw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D57nrMT351fw&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=6e566c46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=57nrMT351fw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 官方表示，《犬夜叉 奈落之戰》精心忠於動畫原著，不僅採用動畫原班聲優日語配音，所有遊戲情節也都原汁原味還原動畫劇情；並將許多動畫片段鏡頭融入遊戲過程中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/57/493117493b4f119adb472d46b314j2l5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F57%2F493117493b4f119adb472d46b314j2l5.JPG&h=b03591be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/62/942ffadab28dbc67ada39299b314j2q5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F62%2F942ffadab28dbc67ada39299b314j2q5.JPG&h=ca36bea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遊戲中也加入了一些特色系統，讓玩家能夠與人氣角色進行互動。「許願樹」將是玩家在遊戲初期就可以體會到的特殊功能。隨著遊戲中劇情的推進，主角們不時會將自己的心願寫下來懸掛在風鈴上，襯著風鈴的叮噹聲響，訴說心聲。<br />\n <br />\n  玩家進入許願樹功能後，可以點擊主角的風鈴，查看繫在風鈴上寫著心願的便籤，並依據自己的判斷回覆角色，進而增加與角色間的親密度。<br />\n <br />\n  而包含許願樹玩法在內，遊戲中還有更多增加角色親密度的內容，隨著參與每一個功能，增加角色互動的親密度，還將能夠解鎖更多例如洗澡系統在內意想不到的玩法內容。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/66/18cbdd197981631b85c0b4d01d14j2u5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F66%2F18cbdd197981631b85c0b4d01d14j2u5.JPG&h=364d2f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M45xBPbBJlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM45xBPbBJlA&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=31188de1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M45xBPbBJlA</a>"},{"pid":"f231cd77b15263c2e39d71bda58d392d7e8e29a9","tid":1106174,"uid":54085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/63/bb135799887d6cfd9bd3c368ac14j2r5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F63%2Fbb135799887d6cfd9bd3c368ac14j2r5.JPG&h=57a3d968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/65/18bf4e4d004c8ca4b93f89a44214j2t5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F65%2F18bf4e4d004c8ca4b93f89a44214j2t5.JPG&h=578c72a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/55/542a47cf1480cc5744402eda2214j2j5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F55%2F542a47cf1480cc5744402eda2214j2j5.JPG&h=2ceede15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/60/4758d0c67b51967c9d7909c7ff14j2o5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F60%2F4758d0c67b51967c9d7909c7ff14j2o5.JPG&h=264ffa0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/56/ebfa83794cdc13c45ed3f5307a14j2k5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F56%2Febfa83794cdc13c45ed3f5307a14j2k5.JPG&h=6d207769&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed0198c74cc61036f5e1898f90eb3557e48e0222","tid":1106174,"uid":54085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"登錄LINK:<a href